<div>
    <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl mb-6">
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-lime-400 via-emerald-400 to-cyan-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Changelog</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-8">
            Notable changes to Soli, newest first. Each release is a section below &mdash;
            the <strong class="text-white">Unreleased</strong> block collects everything on
            <code class="text-cyan-400">main</code> since the last tag. For the raw commit-level
            history see <code class="text-cyan-400">CHANGELOG.md</code> in the repository.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- ===================================================================
         Add a new <section id="vX-Y-Z"> ... </section> ABOVE "Unreleased"
         (newest first) when a version is cut. Version headings are <h2> so
         they appear in the "On this page" rail automatically.
    ==================================================================== -->

    <section id="unreleased" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-24">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline gap-x-4 gap-y-1 mb-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Unreleased</h2>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-lime-400 bg-lime-400/10 border border-lime-400/20 rounded-full px-3 py-0.5">in progress</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">The current development cycle. Grouped by area; jump to a section:</p>

        <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-10 text-sm">
            <a href="#u-realtime" class="rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-3 py-1.5 text-gray-300 hover:text-white hover:border-white/20">Real-time &amp; LiveView</a>
            <a href="#u-ai" class="rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-3 py-1.5 text-gray-300 hover:text-white hover:border-white/20">AI &amp; Search</a>
            <a href="#u-api" class="rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-3 py-1.5 text-gray-300 hover:text-white hover:border-white/20">API</a>
